LABEL: Post
Caption:
Boa tarde domingo, seu lindo! 💗
Muito friozinho por aqui, e por aí? ❄️
Amores, deixa eu compartilhar uma dica com vocês, ultimamente, por conta da gravidez, tenho me preocupado muito em hidratar meu corpo, principalmente as regiões do bumbum, coxas, barriga e seios, que são os lugares mais propícios a aparecer as tão temidas estrias. 😩 E o creme que tem estado comigo atualmente é o da @100estrias, ele é um preventivo para estrias com hidratação intensiva, aplico ele 2 vezes ao dia - de manhã e à noite - e até agora esta tudo sob controle, estrias ZERO por aqui! 🙏🏻😂
Mas, lembrando que para um melhor resultado, tenha sempre uma alimentação saudável e beba muita água por dia!!! 💪🏻#FicaDica
E vocês gravidinhas, o que fazem para prevenir as estrias? Vamos compartilhar nossos truques! 🤰🏼

LABEL: Post
Caption:
It took me just two minutes to collect all these cigarette butts at the Wiggle X Adidas Parley Beach Clean. Did you know cigarette butts are made of plastic? I also found plastic bottles, old lighters, plastic cutlery, straws and cotton ear bud sticks.
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
Most of us are privileged enough to have the power to say no to all these items and opt for more sustainable alternatives so that they don’t end up in our oceans.
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
Thanks @Wiggle_Sport and @TheFinalStrawSolent for organising this beach clean. It's crucial that powerful brands like @adidaslondon recognise the importance of raising awareness of plastic pollution and begin to turn the tide on fast fashion.
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
#WiggleBeachClean #WiggleGetThere #AdidasParley #RunForTheOceans #UltraBoost #2minutebeachclean
#fashionrevolution #ad

LABEL: Post
Caption: Can't leave the house without a spritz -  I just added this beautiful fragrance by @tizianaterenzi  to my collection and this one’s a Gem. Inspired by the black Moon, The Eclix is just pure art from the black bottle topped with a jewel-shaped cap. It starts off with notes of vanilla, almond and tangerine and slowly transforms into more floral where the violet and white lily becomes rich and you smell hints of sandalwood, musk and amber as it develops. It’s reminiscent of something familiar but not quite and that’s what makes it all the more special. It's available in stores at @barneysny and online at the @fragrancegroup site ((link in my bio)). If you get a chance to try this one, I’d love to know what impression it left on you. #ad

LABEL: Post
Caption:
Werbung ✨ Es gibt Tage, da denke ich, dass ich in einem falschen Film aufgewacht bin. Gestern war so einer. Angefangen hat es damit, dass mein Kater Findus die Rosen aufgefressen hat, die mein Schlafzimmer so schön geschmückt haben 🌹😾 Dann stand ich vorm Kleiderschrank und hatte wieder nichts zum anziehen, obwohl der Kleiderschrank voll ist. Wer kennt wohl dieses Problem nicht? 🤷🏼‍♀️ Ich ahnte schon, dass wenn der Tag so anfängt, es später auch nicht besser wird. Und wie recht ich damit hatte! Ich habe plötzlich so viele kurzfristige Jobs und Termine bekommen, dass ich dem ganzen gar nicht hinterher gekommen bin. Und dann dachte ich: lass bitte diesen Tag so schnell wie möglich vorbei sein! Ich würde ihn am liebsten wegwischen! 🙈 An solchen Tagen würde ich gerne alle Termine absagen, Handy stummschalten und mich unter die warme Dusche stellen, um das Ganze runterzuspülen! 💦
•
#ad #foamie #foamit @foamie_official @dm_deutschland

LABEL: Post
Caption:
Gutenmorgen 🌹
Welche Haarpflege benutzt du? Probierst du gern neues aus oder bleibst du bei einer Marke? Ich teste zur Zeit die #guhl Repair&Balance Reihe mit Manuka Honig & Milch und Hydro-Protein-Komplex. ➡Weisst du wie man Shampoo am besten aufträgt?

Bevor du dein Shampoo im feuchten Haar verteilst, solltest du dies zunächst in deine Handfläche geben und dort kurz aufschäumen. Das hat den Vorteil, dass es sich so besser und einfacher im Haar verteilen lässt. Übrigens: Dein Haar wird nicht sauberer, wenn du mehr Shampoo benutzt, ganz im Gegenteil – wenn du sparsam mit deinem Shampoo umgehst, kannst du es anschließend auch besser auswaschen und es verbleiben weniger Rückstände im Haar. 🌹 Das Guhl Shampoo pflegt und revitalisiert die Kopfhaut, verbessert die Haarfaser von innen heraus. ➡ Und wie benutzt man die Spülung am besten ? 
Für perfekte Ergebnisse wird die Spülung beginnend von der Kopfhaut bis in die Spitzen eingearbeitet und gründlich ausgespült. Für Geschmeidigkeit und extra-leichte Kämmbarkeit, ohne zu beschweren. 🌹 Die Pflege-Spülung von Guhl kräftigt die Haarfaser und schenkt Geschmeidigkeit und extra-leichte Kämmbarkeit.

LABEL: Post
Caption:
Dolls, let’s talk beauty! I want to talk about the @farsalicare Unicorn Essence which has officially become my beauty must-have. I have a normal skin type, but I have noticed patches & with this serum, my foundation is even and smooth. Now the @sephoracollection Sephora PRO Warm Palette - I used the colors "Ochre - Brass -Sepia". The pigments are amazing and the color choices are even better. I felt like this palette is perfect for everyday simple looks, but you can totally use it to pull off a look for the night out too. The @theouai Wave Spray was quite interesting for me as a hair enthusiast. YES, I recommend using the spray & using pin-curls for a lovely volumized "oldies" look. The spray gives A LOT of texture!! For this look, I wanted to do soft, small waves, but I am looking forward to doing an IG live on the oldies hair look! What do you all think? 
I got all of these products at Sephora inside @JCPenney #SephoraInJCP #ad

Não tem nada que nos faça sentir mais equilibrados com as nossas energias do que explorar esse mundo e todos seus encantos.
As pulseiras da @livelokai guardam água do Monte Evereste, o ponto mais alto do nosso planeta e lama do Mar Morto, que é o ponto mais baixo.
Ter elas com a gente nos faz lembrar de mantermos sempre a esperança nos momentos mais difíceis e humildade nos momentos de glória
.
.

O que te faz encontrar seu equilíbrio?
#findyourbalance #livelokai #ad .
.
.

There's nothing that helps us find balance like exploring our earth and it's many wonders. @LiveLokai bracelets are filled with water from Mt Everest, the highest point on earth and mud from the Dead Sea, the lowest point. We love that these elements always remind us to stay hopeful through life's lows and humble through the highs. 
How do you find balance? 🌀

LABEL: Post
Caption: #ad As a kid, my absolute favorite book was Goodnight Moon. I still have my childhood copy, which I received on my first birthday. I had the thing memorized before I could even read, so naturally when Iris’ first birthday rolled around, my gift to her was a copy of her very own. I feel like life has come full-circle, now that she can read it to me. I love that childhood books hold more than just the story – they hold memories. And now I get to share those with Iris. This month we’ve teamed up with @pizzahut for The Literacy Project, which provides books to millions of children nationwide. So what’s your favorite childhood book? Share yours, and your memories reading it, in a post of your own with the hashtags #helpstartanewchapter and #sweepstakes to be entered to win an all-expenses paid trip to bring your favorite childhood book to life.

LABEL: Post
Caption:
Working out doesn’t have to mean fancy gym memberships or expensive pieces of equipment! Where I live, Gyms are either too expensive for what they have to offer, or too far away! I’m a home workout kinda gal 😉
•
Stoked about my new equipment! A bar + 200lbs (or so, I need to recount) in weight for....$65 😲 No. it’s not like those sweet @roguefitness plates, but it works, and it was a steal! Our Caring Center is like a Salvation Army. I stopped by there to find stuff for Allys Halloween costume. I love perusing the isles to see what others get rid of 😊 Ive been wanting a bar & plates FOREVER, but I am too cheap to pay full price 😂 They had the bar & 100lbs of weights for $50! Couldn’t have been more excited!
•
I had to go to Goodwill in the town next to us, and guess what I found? A ton more weights that fit my bar! The 8s, 10s, 15s, & 20s were $6 each! And guess what! They were marked with red tags, and not only was it red tag sale day, It was 75% off all red tagged items! Each plate ended up being $1.50!
•
No shame in my resale shopping game. I can’t stand people who turn up their noses to resale items. If this is you, sorry....😂obviously, there are boundaries 😂😂
•
With the exception of the medicine balls and MMA gear, everything has been found at yard sales or resale shops! A lot of them were brand new, still with tags on them! Jayson had the 50lb & 20lb dumbbells when I moved in. Otherwise, I’ve found: a bosu ball, stability balls, brand new workout mats, resistance bands/loops, dumbbells, a pull up bar, kettlebells, and more!
•
@idealfit Peach Lemonade BCAAs in the shaker 🤤 Keyhole Muscle tank in Mauve and core leggings in Navy - hit the link in my bio to see the entire clothing collection! Use code DIANE for 10% off
•
•
•

LABEL: Post
Caption:
I need you. ♡
⠀⠀
A phrase that we’re taught shows weakness. “Need?” Nope, not allowed. We’re supposed to figure it all out on our own...right?
⠀⠀
I need you. ♡
⠀⠀
Three, tiny but powerful words. Words that are freeing, heart opening, and vulnerable. Words that empower trust and safe space, healthy boundaries and deep seeded authenticity.
⠀⠀
I need you @aldensteimle. ♡
I need your support when I’m lost, your kindness when I’m critical, your ability to celebrate me when I’m killing it and hug me when I blow it. I need you and our sisterhood to get through this life, and I feel stronger for saying it.
⠀⠀
Thank you @roxy for celebrating sisterhood and the women who embody it. ♡
📷: @kat_reynolds
#roxyxsister #ad

LABEL: Post
Caption:
This past week the hubby and I had the pleasure to visit one of our favorite places in the Los Angeles-Southern California area, @unistudios . .
.
Over the years, he and I have visited Universal Studios many times individually and together we have been 3 times now. .
.
Some of the favorite features have been there for years and some, are fairly new. There is always something new to experience making the visit always worth it. .
.

Our visit this time was well timed with the Chinese Lunar New Year. Universal Studios is well decorated for this holiday with a full courtyard decked out in traditional red colors, including Lanterns, Pink Cherry Blossom trees which included wish/prayer cards you could attach to the tree. A live stage show for the family discussing ancient Chinese stories read out loud by costumed actors and involving audience members with props to make it a fun show for the whole family.
.
.

In addition to the Lunar New Year celebrations, the park is full of dozens of attraction and rides including the new The Wizarding World of Harry Potter. Watch my feed over the next several days to see a separate post exclusively about that. .

The tour is as fun as ever, with the usual back lot tram tour. Then there were the rides! I have yet to experience a ride that is not a ton of fun. In fact, some of the rides were so thrilling that they had me pretty scared..lol. .
.The shows such as the Special Effects, Water World, Kung Fu Panda & the Scary Walking dead all were worth doing all over again. So much so, that we are already talking about when to go back again.
.
.

As I said, stay tuned for my special post about The Wizarding World of Harry Potter. As this was all new to me and there was so much to see and experience, I am doing a full separate post just about that part of the park! .
.
If you have been to Universal Studios Hollywood, I would love to hear what you thought. What was your favorite part of the park? .
.
#sponsored #whenincalifornia #californiabound  #awmyposh #travelwAW #californiagram #wheninhollywood
#UniversalStudiosHollywood
#wizardingworldhollywood
#CityWalkLA #hellokitty

Caption:
We experienced the new Kung Fu Panda Adventure ride at Universal Studios Hollywood today and it was so much fun!!! _______
It’s a motion simulator with each seat moving according to the adventure. You go down a river, experience Po fighting and you even get splashed a bit with water. It’s a fun story line and the line goes fast because there’s so many seats in the theatre. 
_______
Outside the theater, you can meet and greet with Po and Tigress at Universal Plaza and stop by Mr. Ping’s Noodle Shop to enjoy his authentic Asian fare and a selection of hot and cold Asian beverages.
_______
Check out my stories for a clip of the adventure!!!
_______

.

.
